t=\"#feedbackModal_main_3612070\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104bcn1665702597290.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bcn1665702597290.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/bcn1665702597290.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100277e1_d100278e1_d100279e1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"bcn1665702597290\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100277e1_d100278e1_d100279e1\">\n      \n                                               InheritWinProps\n                                             </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Form instance property of a popup form that determines whether the it inherits the window properties that have been explicitly defined for the form. It can be set in ProcScript using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span>. Valid values: <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code> (default).\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__topic_d100280e1_d100281e1_d100282e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100283e1_d100284e1_d100285e1\">InheritWinProps\n                                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">= \"\n                                         <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">true</code>\n                                       \"</code> | \"<code class=\"ph codeph\">false</code>\"</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__section_w4419ab1b5b3_w4420ab1b5_w4421ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1__entry__2\">\n The form's window properties are set to the defaults for a popup window. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rhe1665702581016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rhe1665702581016.html\" title=\"A popup window displays a form in a secondary window that is anchored to a field. The position of the popup window is configurable, so that it can be displayed outside or inside the boundaries of its parent field.\">Popup Window</a>.\n                                                   </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"bcn1665702597290__table_d11702e1_d11703e1_d11704e1__entry__2\">\n The window properties that have been explicitly set for the form are inherited.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__section_w4422ab1b5b5_w4423ab1b5_w4424ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d481605e140\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100289e1_d100290e1_d100291e1\">This property can only be set when using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span> ProcScript statement to create a component instance in a popup window.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__section_ppb_kqy_swb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d481605e152\">Example: InheritWinProps </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100295e1_d100296e1_d100297e1\">For example, the following codes activates a form\n            in a popup window to the right of the field, and inherits other window properties:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__pre_qz2_nqy_swb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;DETAIL trigger of FLD1\nnewinstance DETAIL_FRM, \"Details\", \"windowtype=popup<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>InheritWinProps=true<span class=\"ph gold\">;</span>position=BOTTOMRIGHT_UPRIGHT\"\nactivate \"Details\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100298e1_d100299e1_d100300e1\">If DETAIL_FRM is defined as a normal form, with the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Caption</span> and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Close</span> properties selected,\n            the popup form will be displayed with a title bar that has a close button.</p>\n<div class=\"p\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__p_d100301e1_d100302e1_d100303e1\">\n<figure class=\"fig fignone\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__fig_sz2_nqy_swb\">\n<img alt=\"image\" class=\"image\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__image_g1y_pqy_swb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/popupforminheritwinprops.png?_LANG=enus\"/>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section ul\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__section_w4425ab1b5b9_w4426ab1b5_w4427ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d481605e191\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"bcn1665702597290__li_d40487e1_d40488e1_d40489e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a> (<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rhe1665702581016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rhe1665702581016.html\" title=\"A popup window displays a form in a secondary window that is anchored to a field. The position of the popup window is configurable, so that it can be displayed outside or inside the boundaries of its parent field.\">Popup Window</a>)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612070\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612070\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "InheritWinProps Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 InheritWinProps Form instance property of a popup form that determines whether the it inherits the window properties that have been explicitly defined for the form. It can be set in ProcScript using newinstance . Valid values: True or False (default). InheritWinProps = \" true \" | \" false \" Value Description False The form's window properties are set to the defaults for a popup window. For more information, see Popup Window . True The window properties that have been explicitly set for the form are inherited. Description This property can only be set when using the newinstance ProcScript statement to create a component instance in a popup window. Example: InheritWinProps For example, the following codes activates a form in a popup window to the right of the field, and inherits other window properties: ;DETAIL trigger of FLD1 newinstance DETAIL_FRM, \"Details\", \"windowtype=popup ; InheritWinProps=true ; position=BOTTOMRIGHT_UPRIGHT\" activate \"Details\" Copy If DETAIL_FRM is defined as a normal form, with the Caption and Close properties selected, the popup form will be displayed with a title bar that has a close button. Applies To Form ( Popup Window ) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}